{"chapter": 0, "title": "脂砚斋重评石头记凡例", "pages": [{"page": 9, "width": 516.0, "height": 729.0, "blocks": [{"type": 0, "number": 0, "bbox": [73.7, 684.0, 260.2, 694.2], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 684.0, 81.1, 685.0], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "www.hlmbbs.com ", "size": 0.9599999785423279, "font": "TimesNewRoman", "color": 16777215, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.890999972820282, "descender": -0.2160000056028366, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 684.8], "bbox": [73.7, 684.0, 81.1, 685.0]}]}, {"bbox": [73.7, 685.2, 73.9, 686.2], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": " ", "size": 0.9599999785423279, "font": "TimesNewRoman", "color": 16777215, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.890999972820282, "descender": -0.2160000056028366, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 686.0], "bbox": [73.7, 685.2, 73.9, 686.2]}]}, {"bbox": [255.7, 684.3, 260.2, 694.2], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "1", "size": 9.0, "font": "TimesNewRoman", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.890999972820282, "descender": -0.2160000056028366, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [255.7, 692.3], "bbox": [255.7, 684.3, 260.2, 694.2]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 1, "bbox": [73.7, 80.2, 79.7, 92.2], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 80.2, 79.7, 92.2], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": " ", "size": 12.0, "font": "ºÚÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 90.5], "bbox": [73.7, 80.2, 79.7, 92.2]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 2, "bbox": [73.7, 102.1, 358.9, 136.6], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 102.1, 79.7, 114.1], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": " ", "size": 12.0, "font": "ºÚÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 112.4], "bbox": [73.7, 102.1, 79.7, 114.1]}]}, {"bbox": [163.0, 118.6, 343.7, 136.6], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "脂砚斋重评石头记凡例", "size": 18.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [163.0, 134.0], "bbox": [163.0, 118.6, 343.7, 136.6]}]}, {"bbox": [343.8, 117.3, 358.9, 135.7], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "①", "size": 9.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [343.8, 125.0], "bbox": [343.8, 117.3, 352.8, 126.3]}, {"text": " ", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [352.9, 134.0], "bbox": [352.9, 123.7, 358.9, 135.7]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 3, "bbox": [73.7, 147.5, 79.7, 159.5], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 147.5, 79.7, 159.5], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": " ", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 157.8], "bbox": [73.7, 147.5, 79.7, 159.5]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 4, "bbox": [73.7, 169.6, 79.7, 181.6], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 169.6, 79.7, 181.6], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": " ", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 179.9], "bbox": [73.7, 169.6, 79.7, 181.6]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 5, "bbox": [73.7, 191.5, 442.3, 203.5], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 191.5, 442.3, 203.5], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "  《红楼梦》旨义 是书题名极[多，一曰《红楼]", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 201.8], "bbox": [73.7, 191.5, 349.0, 203.5]}, {"text": "②", "size": 9.960000038146973, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [349.0, 201.8], "bbox": [349.0, 193.3, 358.9, 203.2]}, {"text": "梦》，是总其全", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [359.0, 201.8], "bbox": [359.0, 191.5, 442.3, 203.5]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 6, "bbox": [73.7, 213.5, 447.1, 225.5], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 213.5, 447.1, 225.5], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "部之名也；又曰《风月宝鉴》，是戒妄动风月之情；又曰《石头记》，", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 223.8], "bbox": [73.7, 213.5, 447.1, 225.5]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 7, "bbox": [73.7, 235.6, 442.2, 247.6], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 235.6, 442.2, 247.6], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "是自譬石头所记之事也。此三名皆书中曾已点睛矣。如宝玉作梦，梦中", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 245.9], "bbox": [73.7, 235.6, 442.2, 247.6]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 8, "bbox": [73.7, 257.5, 447.1, 269.5], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 257.5, 447.1, 269.5], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "有曲，名曰《红楼梦十二支》，此则《红楼梦》之点睛。又如贾瑞病，", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 267.8], "bbox": [73.7, 257.5, 447.1, 269.5]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 9, "bbox": [73.7, 279.5, 442.2, 291.5], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 279.5, 442.2, 291.5], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "跛道人持一镜来，上面即錾“风月宝鉴”四字，此则《风月宝鉴》之点", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 289.8], "bbox": [73.7, 279.5, 442.2, 291.5]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 10, "bbox": [73.7, 301.6, 442.3, 313.6], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 301.6, 442.3, 313.6], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "睛。又如道人亲眼见石上大书一篇故事，则系石头所记之往来，此则《石", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 311.9], "bbox": [73.7, 301.6, 442.3, 313.6]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 11, "bbox": [73.7, 323.5, 442.2, 335.5], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 323.5, 442.2, 335.5], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "头记》之点睛处。然此书又名曰《金陵十二钗》，审其名，则必系金陵", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 333.8], "bbox": [73.7, 323.5, 442.2, 335.5]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 12, "bbox": [73.7, 345.5, 442.1, 357.5], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 345.5, 442.1, 357.5], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "十二女子也；然通部细搜检去，上中下女子岂止十二人哉！若云其中自", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 355.8], "bbox": [73.7, 345.5, 442.1, 357.5]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 13, "bbox": [73.7, 367.6, 442.1, 379.6], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 367.6, 442.1, 379.6], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "有十二个，则又未尝指明白系某某，及至“红楼梦”一回中，亦曾翻出", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 377.9], "bbox": [73.7, 367.6, 442.1, 379.6]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 14, "bbox": [73.7, 389.5, 296.6, 401.5], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 389.5, 296.6, 401.5], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "金陵十二钗之簿籍，又有十二支曲可考。 ", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 399.8], "bbox": [73.7, 389.5, 296.6, 401.5]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 15, "bbox": [73.7, 411.5, 442.3, 423.5], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 411.5, 442.3, 423.5], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "  书中凡写长安，在文人笔墨之间，则从古之称；凡愚夫妇、儿女子", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 421.8], "bbox": [73.7, 411.5, 442.3, 423.5]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 16, "bbox": [73.7, 433.6, 442.3, 445.6], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 433.6, 442.3, 445.6], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "家常口角，则曰“中京”，是不欲着迹于方向也。盖天子之邦，亦当以", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 443.9], "bbox": [73.7, 433.6, 442.3, 445.6]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 17, "bbox": [73.7, 455.5, 272.5, 467.5], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 455.5, 272.5, 467.5], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "中为尊，特避其东南西北四字样也。 ", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 465.8], "bbox": [73.7, 455.5, 272.5, 467.5]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 18, "bbox": [73.7, 477.5, 442.2, 489.5], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 477.5, 442.2, 489.5], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "  此书只是着意于闺中，故叙闺中之事切，略涉于外事者则简，不得", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 487.8], "bbox": [73.7, 477.5, 442.2, 489.5]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 19, "bbox": [73.7, 499.6, 152.0, 511.6], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 499.6, 152.0, 511.6], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "谓其不均也。 ", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 509.9], "bbox": [73.7, 499.6, 152.0, 511.6]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 20, "bbox": [73.7, 521.5, 442.2, 533.5], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 521.5, 442.2, 533.5], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "  此书不敢干涉朝廷，凡有不得不用朝政者，只略用一笔带出，盖实", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 531.8], "bbox": [73.7, 521.5, 442.2, 533.5]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 21, "bbox": [73.7, 543.5, 381.0, 555.5], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 543.5, 381.0, 555.5], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "不敢以写儿女之笔墨唐突朝廷之上也，又不得谓其不备。 ", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 553.8], "bbox": [73.7, 543.5, 381.0, 555.5]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 22, "bbox": [73.7, 565.6, 442.2, 577.6], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 565.6, 442.2, 577.6], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "  此书开卷第一回也，作者自云：因曾历过一番梦幻之后，故将真事", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 575.9], "bbox": [73.7, 565.6, 442.2, 577.6]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 23, "bbox": [73.7, 587.5, 442.3, 599.5], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 587.5, 442.3, 599.5], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "隐去，而撰此《石头记》一书也。故曰“甄士隐梦幻识通灵”。但书中", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 597.8], "bbox": [73.7, 587.5, 442.3, 599.5]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 24, "bbox": [73.7, 609.5, 442.2, 621.5], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 609.5, 442.2, 621.5], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "所记何事？又因何而撰是书哉？自云：今风尘碌碌，一事无成，忽念及", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 619.8], "bbox": [73.7, 609.5, 442.2, 621.5]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 25, "bbox": [73.7, 631.6, 442.1, 643.6], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 631.6, 442.1, 643.6], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "当日所有之女子，一一细推了去，觉其行止见识皆出于我之上，何堂堂", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 641.9], "bbox": [73.7, 631.6, 442.1, 643.6]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 26, "bbox": [73.7, 653.5, 442.2, 665.5], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 653.5, 442.2, 665.5], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "之须眉诚不若彼一干裙钗？实愧则有馀，悔则无益之大无可奈何之日", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 663.8], "bbox": [73.7, 653.5, 442.2, 665.5]}]}]}]}, {"page": 10, "width": 516.0, "height": 729.0, "blocks": [{"type": 0, "number": 0, "bbox": [208.2, 52.3, 312.2, 61.3], "lines": [{"bbox": [208.2, 52.3, 312.2, 61.3], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "抚琴居红楼梦脂评汇校本 ", "size": 9.0, "font": "¿¬Ìå_GB2312", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [208.2, 60.0], "bbox": [208.2, 52.3, 312.2, 61.3]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 1, "bbox": [73.7, 685.2, 80.8, 686.2], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 685.2, 80.8, 686.2], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "redactor: kolistan ", "size": 0.9599999785423279, "font": "TimesNewRoman", "color": 16777215, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.890999972820282, "descender": -0.2160000056028366, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 686.0], "bbox": [73.7, 685.2, 80.8, 686.2]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 2, "bbox": [255.7, 685.3, 260.2, 695.3], "lines": [{"bbox": [255.7, 685.3, 260.2, 695.3], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "2", "size": 9.0, "font": "TimesNewRoman", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.890999972820282, "descender": -0.2160000056028366, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [255.7, 693.4], "bbox": [255.7, 685.3, 260.2, 695.3]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 3, "bbox": [73.7, 80.2, 442.3, 92.2], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 80.2, 442.3, 92.2], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "也。当此时，则自欲将已往所赖——上赖天恩，下承祖德，锦衣纨袴之", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 90.5], "bbox": [73.7, 80.2, 442.3, 92.2]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 4, "bbox": [73.7, 102.1, 442.3, 114.1], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 102.1, 442.3, 114.1], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "时，饫甘餍美之日，背父母教育之恩，负师兄规训之德，以致今日一事", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 112.4], "bbox": [73.7, 102.1, 442.3, 114.1]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 5, "bbox": [73.7, 124.2, 447.1, 136.2], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 124.2, 447.1, 136.2], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "无成、半生潦倒之罪，编述一记，以告普天下人。虽我之罪固不能免，", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 134.5], "bbox": [73.7, 124.2, 447.1, 136.2]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 6, "bbox": [73.7, 146.2, 442.2, 158.2], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 146.2, 442.2, 158.2], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "然闺阁中本自历历有人，万不可因我不肖，则一并使其泯灭也。虽今日", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 156.5], "bbox": [73.7, 146.2, 442.2, 158.2]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 7, "bbox": [73.7, 168.1, 442.3, 180.1], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 168.1, 442.3, 180.1], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "之茅椽蓬牖，瓦灶绳床，其风晨月夕，阶柳庭花，亦未有伤于我之襟怀", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 178.4], "bbox": [73.7, 168.1, 442.3, 180.1]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 8, "bbox": [73.7, 190.2, 442.3, 202.2], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 190.2, 442.3, 202.2], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "笔墨者。何为不用假语村言敷演出一段故事来，以悦人之耳目哉？故曰", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 200.5], "bbox": [73.7, 190.2, 442.3, 202.2]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 9, "bbox": [73.7, 212.2, 442.1, 224.2], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 212.2, 442.1, 224.2], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "“[贾雨村]风尘怀闺秀”，乃是第一回题纲正义也。开卷即云“风尘怀", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 222.5], "bbox": [73.7, 212.2, 442.1, 224.2]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 10, "bbox": [73.7, 234.1, 447.1, 246.1], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 234.1, 447.1, 246.1], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "闺秀”，则知作者本意原为记述当日闺友闺情，并非怨世骂时之书矣。", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 244.4], "bbox": [73.7, 234.1, 447.1, 246.1]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 11, "bbox": [73.7, 256.2, 441.1, 268.2], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 256.2, 441.1, 268.2], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "虽一时有涉于世态，然亦不得不叙者，但非其本旨耳。阅者切记之。 ", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 266.5], "bbox": [73.7, 256.2, 441.1, 268.2]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 12, "bbox": [73.7, 278.2, 140.0, 290.2], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 278.2, 140.0, 290.2], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "  诗曰： ", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 288.5], "bbox": [73.7, 278.2, 140.0, 290.2]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 13, "bbox": [73.7, 300.1, 320.6, 312.1], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 300.1, 320.6, 312.1], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "    浮生着甚苦奔忙，盛席华筵终散场。 ", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 310.4], "bbox": [73.7, 300.1, 320.6, 312.1]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 14, "bbox": [73.7, 322.2, 320.6, 334.2], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 322.2, 320.6, 334.2], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "    悲喜千般同幻渺，古今一梦尽荒唐。 ", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 332.5], "bbox": [73.7, 322.2, 320.6, 334.2]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 15, "bbox": [73.7, 344.2, 320.6, 356.2], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 344.2, 320.6, 356.2], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "    谩言红袖啼痕重，更有情痴抱恨长。 ", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 354.5], "bbox": [73.7, 344.2, 320.6, 356.2]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 16, "bbox": [73.7, 366.1, 320.6, 378.1], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 366.1, 320.6, 378.1], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "    字字看来皆是血，十年辛苦不寻常。 ", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 376.4], "bbox": [73.7, 366.1, 320.6, 378.1]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 17, "bbox": [73.7, 388.2, 79.7, 400.2], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 388.2, 79.7, 400.2], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": " ", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 398.5], "bbox": [73.7, 388.2, 79.7, 400.2]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 18, "bbox": [73.7, 410.8, 442.2, 422.8], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 410.8, 442.2, 422.8], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "  ", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 421.1], "bbox": [73.7, 410.8, 91.8, 422.8]}, {"text": "①按：此凡例五条仅见于甲戌本卷首；其他各本均无凡例，且均截取第五条“此", "size": 9.960000038146973, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [97.8, 421.1], "bbox": [97.8, 412.5, 442.2, 422.5]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 19, "bbox": [73.7, 432.7, 270.6, 444.7], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 432.7, 270.6, 444.7], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "开卷第一回也”并入第一回作为正文开始。", "size": 9.960000038146973, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 443.0], "bbox": [73.7, 434.5, 264.5, 444.4]}, {"text": " ", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [264.6, 443.0], "bbox": [264.6, 432.7, 270.6, 444.7]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 20, "bbox": [73.7, 454.8, 442.2, 466.8], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 454.8, 442.2, 466.8], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "  ", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 465.1], "bbox": [73.7, 454.8, 91.8, 466.8]}, {"text": "②此处原被撕去一角，缺五字。胡适补“多”“红楼”三字，吴恩裕另校补“一", "size": 9.960000038146973, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [97.8, 465.1], "bbox": [97.8, 456.6, 442.2, 466.5]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 21, "bbox": [73.7, 477.7, 407.8, 489.4], "lines": [{"bbox": [73.7, 477.7, 407.8, 489.4], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": "曰”两字。除“红楼”二字无争议外，前三字所补是否恰当，有不同意见。", "size": 9.960000038146973, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [73.7, 487.1], "bbox": [73.7, 478.5, 405.0, 488.5]}, {"text": " ", "size": 10.5600004196167, "font": "TimesNewRoman,Bold", "color": 0, "flags": 20, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.890999972820282, "descender": -0.2160000056028366, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 24, "origin": [405.1, 487.1], "bbox": [405.1, 477.7, 407.8, 489.4]}]}]}, {"type": 0, "number": 22, "bbox": [257.9, 498.1, 263.9, 510.1], "lines": [{"bbox": [257.9, 498.1, 263.9, 510.1], "wmode": 0, "dir": [1.0, 0.0], "spans": [{"text": " ", "size": 12.0, "font": "ËÎÌå", "color": 0, "flags": 4, "alpha": 255, "ascender": 0.859000027179718, "descender": -0.14000000059604645, "bidi": 0, "char_flags": 16, "origin": [257.9, 508.4], "bbox": [257.9, 498.1, 263.9, 510.1]}]}]}]}]}